USWNT legend @carlilloyd announces her retirement 🐐⬇️

She will play her last matches for the USWNT this fall and will finish the NWSL season with Gotham FC.

—2x World Cup
—2x Olympic Gold 
—2x FIFA Women’s player of the year
—Second most-capped USWNT player
—128 international goals
—One World Cup final hat-trick

What a career 👏
